# Plan Outline

By 2028 complete:

* Detailed plans for implementation of NLNM (Non-Lethal, Non-Mutilating, No Serious Injury) combat. It must successfully prove for  feasibility implementation of NLNM on a concrete schedule.
* Based on analysis, create a goal based roadmap.  High level proposal 3 stages of 33/4 years  with full implementation coming in 100 years (2128).   Schedule will be adjustable based on the goals reached in the roadmap.
* Create a realistic working simulation of tactical combat up to regiment level.
